	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Per Iesum Christum omnem salutem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scripsi nuper <persName ref="person59">Benedicti Euandri</persName> causa ad te<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Siehe oben <ref target="file10284">Nr. 253</ref>.</note>, frater sincerissime, nunc iterum ecclesie nostre.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Desperabundi de saluti plurimorum.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Interturbatur ecclesia Lutheranorum, anabaptistarum et aliorum doctrina.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Per decennium predicatur verbum dei<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Seit ungefähr 1523 predigten in <placeName ref="place544">Kempten</placeName> <persName ref="person1976">Sixt Rummel</persName>, <persName ref="person89">Jakob Haistung</persName> und <persName ref="person1962">Johannes Rottach</persName> im evangelischen Geist, s. <hi>Erhard,</hi> Reformation 7f.</note> sine fructu<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Vgl. Mt 13, 22 par.</note>.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Adhuc omnia pendent sub priori seculo.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ceremonie prostant adhuc cum misse nomenclatura in monasterio<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">In dem vor der Stadt liegenden, mächtigen Benediktinerkloster. In der Stadt selbst hatten nur die Nonnen des Franziskanerinnenklosters den katholischen Glauben beibehalten und mußten deshalb 1537 <placeName ref="place544">Kempten</placeName> verlassen, s. <hi>Erhard,</hi> Reformation 41.</note>.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Luditur, bibitur, peieratur etc., nec ulle censure apud seniores populi memoria habetur.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Timent cesarem.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid plura?</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Audiunt verbum dei, sed non credunt<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5">Vgl. Jes 6, 9; Mt 13, 13-23.</note>.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Timeo in damnationis testimonium denuncietur, ut ubique inscius, quid faciendum, ita «sanctum dare canibus» [Mt 7, 6].</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vellem potius esse tecum agro Tigurino, si deus velit.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Consule itaque, optime frater, boni, si quid habes.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ni adsit deus miris modis, decidit omnis spes.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Magistratus timore perculsus.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Misera gens pendet a mense fortuna.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex Christi precepto brevi abeundum censeo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scribito paucis, si vacas, per huius schede latorem<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">Unbekannt.</note>.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ora sedulo nisu pro statu ecclesie nostre, etiam pro nobis.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Itidem et nos faciemus.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cupio salvos fratres omnes, qui tecum sunt, Leonem<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7"><persName ref="person114">Leo Jud</persName>.</note>, <persName ref="person188">Erasmum Fabricium</persName>, <persName ref="person117">Carolstadium</persName>.</s>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutant et te tuosque fratres mei<note xml:id="fn8" type="footnote" n="8"><persName ref="person116">Kappelers</persName> Amtsbrüder <persName ref="person173">Paul Rasdorfer</persName> und <persName ref="person89">Jakob Haistung</persName>.</note>, etiam genitricem tuam<note xml:id="fn9" type="footnote" n="9"><persName ref="person32">Anna Bullinger</persName>, geb. Wiederkehr.</note> cum uxore<note xml:id="fn10" type="footnote" n="10"><persName ref="person32">Anna Bullinger</persName>, geb. Adlischwyler.</note> adamata: omnem gratiam.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><pb type="edition" next="224"/>Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Kampidone, 6. novembris 33, raptim.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vitus Kappeller, verbi dei minister, tuus deditus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="27" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Heinricho Bullingero episcopo Tigurino, viro candido diligentissimoque fratri.</s>
					<s n="28" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Zürich.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
